  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK178">
<l>aḵkāmai celvattiṟ kiyāteṉiṉ veḵkāmai</l>
<l>vēṇṭum piṟaṉkaip poruḷ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If it is weighed, "what is the indestructibility of wealth," it is freedom from covetousness.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
